0594321d73e9fd7974b8d0e333f8064c632109ef.query:
SELECT
                    hashes,
                    size
                FROM
                    files f
                WHERE
                    f.id = $1

64258c3efdcdb95fbd7e8ce063a3014d4e06f37a.query:
INSERT INTO files (
                    id,
                    hashes,
                    size
                )
                VALUES (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3
                )
                ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE SET
                    hashes = EXCLUDED.hashes,
                    size = EXCLUDED.size

f4dd978c01bca792c04fff4eb443b140f64ee216.query:
DELETE FROM
                    files f
                WHERE
                    f.id = $1
